name: FanDuuroMagazine
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, what's in the news?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
This skill lets you listen to the most interesting unbiased tech reviews on the internet. Whether you want to check if a new video game is worth buying or a new piece of tech is as good as they say it is, Duuro Magazine is the place to be.

Now also available on Alexa. Just let Alexa read out the latest news and reviews.

This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Duuro App Studio
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
